                  <rs type="fn" role="other"><rs type="person" ref="#pe__johann_sachs_QGW_II_I_1488"><roleName type="title">her</roleName> Jans der Sachs, <roleName type="occ" corresp="#org__wien-st_niklas_vor_dem_stubentor_zisterzienserinnen-altar_st_niklas">chapellan</roleName> sand Niclas alter in dem vrownchloster dacz sand
